Five years in the state penitentiary was the sentence imposed today by Judge A. C. Hoppmann upon John Schmidt, alien enemy, who pleaded guilty in superior court to attempting murder otherwise than by assault. Schmidt will be taken to Waupun tomorrow by Sheriff Henry R. Ireland.
